<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Photogram</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #262626;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f09433 0%, #e6683c 25%, #dc2743 50%, #cc2366 75%, #bc1888 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #262626;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0095f6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #8e8e8e;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            border-top: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
        }

        .username-highlight {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #bc1888;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Photogram</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to the community, <%= name %>!</h2>
            <p>We're thrilled to have you join Photogram. Start sharing your favorite moments, connecting with friends,
                and discovering amazing creators.</p>
            <p>Your username is: <span class="username-highlight">@<%= username %></span></p>
            <p>Ready to get started? Dive in and set up your profile!</p>
            <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" class="btn">Verify Email</a>
            <a href="<%= frontend %>" class="btn">Take me to Photogram</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Photogram from Hamzah. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You received this email because you signed up for Photogram.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>